overview:
“Cleaner London – friendly, professional lifestyle solutions for both the home and office.

We provide domestic and commercial cleaning to all of the London postcodes, our professional cleaners are fully trained and insured to provide domestic cleaning, carpet cleaning, steam carpet cleaning and commercial cleaning at very competitive prices.

If you need a regular domestic cleaner to look after your home, then we provide you with the very best, are cleaners are friendly, hardworking and will come in on a set day and time which is convenient for you.

If your moving out of your property then why not choose our end of tenancy cleaning service, we provide all of our own equipment so you can be free to get on with what is important. We also provide carpet cleaning services and steam carpet cleaning of bathrooms and kitchens so you can be assured of meeting all the requirements of your end of tenancy clean. Check out our site to see a full range of the cleaning services we provide”
